        <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>


The literal translation of Ikiru is "To Live".        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
In the last scene with Toyo (in the restaurant with the birthday party going on), the position of the bell on the mechanical bunny changes, even though neither actor has touched the bunny.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
                <hr />
    <div id="quotes" class="text-block">
        <h4>Quotes</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0793766/?ref_=tt_trv_qu" ><span class="character">Kanji</span></a>:
Drinking this expensive sake is like paying myself back with poison for the way I lived all these years.
<br />        <a href="trivia?tab=qt&ref_=tt_trv_qu" class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
